ygData.subject: Re: [eqbards] Amp
ygData.msgSnippet: Combine instruments are slightly better than normal instruments -- for the price it s a good deal unless you have better.  sell-back price is around a plat tho
ygData.messageBody:
Combine instruments are slightly better than normal instruments -- for the price it's a good deal unless you have better. sell-back price is around a plat tho so if you do any testing on your own, don't expect much P
Katta is a cool place. undead spawn as you walk thru the graveyards tho -- they were green to me at 56 but they are not decaying skeletons either. Some might have a tough time with them.
